46 Neither death has reached him yet, nor guilt leads him,
47 replied my teacher, to torment him;
48 but to give him full experience,

49 to me, who am dead, it is necessary to lead him
50 through hell here below round and round;
51 and this is true as I speak to you.

61 Then that one foot to turn himself suspended,
